A production error was discovered in table IIA02 and related
electoral division map. The proportions of households where working
age social welfare was majority of household income by electoral
division were incorrect - these proportions were calculated as a
proportion of  persons in the electoral division and not households.
Both table and map were updated on 4/7/19.
